column5: I'm looking to rent a boat in the Windsor area. I was told to check out Mitchell's Bay, but I haven't been successful in locating any information.  Any help would be awesome...thanks...!
Bass haven in the bay 519-354-4242 Dennis or Cathy will treat you right. Plus give you daily knowledge of the bite.
Dennis just added another NEW polar kraft to the fleet. Nice ride if you can get your hands on it !
I believe Stoney Point marina still rents boats heres the # 5197985757 6988 st clair rd stoney point ontario
Looks like I have some calls to make...this is awesome...thanks so much!!
